# {{ company_name }} — Architecture

**Source of truth for HOW the system is built + the cloning guide.** This is
the mother clone: the generic skeleton every `<name>-cs` reuses. The shared
engine is the kernel (`cs-kernel`, import package `cs`); the per-company
variance is entirely in `manifest.toml`, stamped below.

Everything company-specific below is STAMPED from `manifest.toml` by the
`cs-template` copier — do not hand-edit it; change `manifest.toml` and
`copier update` instead (variance lives in the manifest + `company/*.md`,
never in a rendered file).

